title: The Weeknd Featured On Nav's Debut Project Coming This Month
text:
Home > Music > The Weeknd Featured On Nav's Debut Project Coming This Month The Weeknd Featured On Nav's Debut Project Coming This Month 0 0 Posted by Zakk Feig , Feb 11, 2017 at 09:28pm Nav and The Weeknd have a collaboration on the way. 
Nav has been picking up new fans left and right, and it's only going up from here. Today on Instagram, the rising Toronto artist announced that his first project will be arriving by the end of this month. A photo posted by Nav (@beatsbynav) on Feb 11, 2017 at 2:51pm PST 
If that wasn't exciting enough, a certain artist named The Weeknd commented, "the brownboy and the starboy on a track," implying he'll be featured on the upcoming project. 
It's been reported that Nav's upcoming project is separate from his collab album with Metro Boomin , which will be dropping shortly after. 
Which project are y'all more amped for? You can learn more about Nav in our exclusive piece right here .
